    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''City Traffic Pricing Wins U.S. and Spitzer's Favor'' (front page, June 8):</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''City Traffic Pricing Wins U.S. and Spitzer's Favor'' (front page, June 8):</p>
        <p>The only certainties about ''congestion pricing'' are that it's going to generate millions of dollars for politicians to squander, make ordinary folks who have to drive into Manhattan a little poorer, and convince a lot of folks that they're better off spending their money elsewhere.</p>
        <p>Willis Blackburn  New York, June 8, 2007</p>
      </block>
